"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/LDRracing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>Liam Delves<\/strong><\/a> push through a difficult weekend to finish with some solid results, with a tenth-place finish in race one that he then improved on in the second race to finish seventh.<\/p>\n<p>After switching his machine at the previous round, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/jamesbullracing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>James Bull<\/strong><\/a> was still getting to know the new R6 he\u2019s now piloting in the National Junior Superstock Championship, but he\u2019s been making solid progress with the new equipment.<\/p>\n<p>The guys in the <a href=\"https:\/\/trueheroesracing.co.uk\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>True Heroes Racing<\/strong><\/a> camp had a solid weekend of racing in both the Pirelli National Superstock championship and the Ducati Tri-Options Cup.<\/p>\n<p>With just two rounds remaining, it\u2019s all to play for. We can\u2019t wait to see what Donnington Park has in store next weekend as the next Showdown round approaches.<\/p><\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n<\/section>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>With a point to prove, Tommy Bridewell lit up the Bennetts British Superbike Championship at Oulton Park this weekend with two sensational wins, blowing the championship battle wide open as we head towards the end of the season.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":1482,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[1],"tags":[13,27,12],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v19.0 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>BSB \u2013 Oulton Showdown battle opens up the championship - Super Soco<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Tommy Bridewell lit up the British Superbike Championship at Oulton Park with two sensational wins, blowing the championship battle wide open\" 